[DESCRIPTION]
kbattery is a small tool to display battery status. It has been tested on GNU/Linux.

[INSTALL]
Download the source code using git:
git clone git://github.com/XieConnect/kbattery.git

Enter the source code directory and compile:
cd DIRECTORY_OF_KBATTERY
make


[USAGE]
Enter the directory where you compiled kbattery:
cd DIRECTORY_OF_KBATTERY

Run the command:
./kbattery

Here is the sample output:
Now   $$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$     85%
Full  $$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$  100%


